name: Ridow's pizzabaguettes
description:
Ridow starts eating and talking at the same time: "Mmmm... these pizzabaguettes are really tasty! They come with homemade tomatosauce, cheese from the Jumbengo region, and good-good-good squirrel meat" 

"If yao's hongy, there are 10 pizzabaguettis freshleh out de oven fo' u" his brother acquaints you.
